videos.headline: Romney stretches out for big first down grab
videos.description: Zack Wilson passes deep to Gunner Romney, who stretches out to make a 38-yard grab along the sideline to get BYU into the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Romney stretches out for big first down grab) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zach Wilson leads BYU with 4 TDs vs. Western Kentucky
videos.description: Zach Wilson throws for three touchdowns and runs for a fourth in BYU's 41-10 win vs. Western Kentucky.
